{"tid":1307871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果A1: 跆拳黑帶護連儂牆 捱13拳不還手","createTime":"2019-07-11T17:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T05:44:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"662e7e1abbf6e77b2eae9395a9d0881ee3b0400b","tid":1307871,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/66428008_10157833795262448_7198217509940494336_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_oc=AQki-JDmMytL2jKrJPfrtMMVaMDPFBO2JXXueijEUKPWFaa1y5t3N3VQ0KPAfd4Xnsc&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=c1ffd484608c637adecff5fa8cb232ff&amp;oe=5DC2AEAC\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F66428008_10157833795262448_7198217509940494336_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_oc%3DAQki-JDmMytL2jKrJPfrtMMVaMDPFBO2JXXueijEUKPWFaa1y5t3N3VQ0KPAfd4Xnsc%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Dc1ffd484608c637adecff5fa8cb232ff%26oe%3D5DC2AEAC&h=9a10cab0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d789cd8938305353990d3a864eeada63aea70ce6","tid":1307871,"uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:39:53.000Z","msg":"【A1頭條】以和平方式表達訴求的連儂牆遍地開花，連日來卻有反對者惡意破壞。36歲義工阿麥與65歲李伯，昨凌晨看守九龍灣連儂牆期間，一名男子踩場撕毀牆上心意貼，他們上前阻止時，先後遭對方揮拳襲擊，男子拳拳到肉，以粗言辱罵義工，本身是跆拳道黑帶的阿麥，全程不閃避不還手，結果慘捱13拳倒地。警方接報到場將涉嫌施襲者拘捕，事後控以兩項襲擊致造成實際身體傷害罪，下周五在觀塘裁判法院提堂。民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇直斥施襲者是「人渣」。"},{"pid":"444c1db5703c1e1bf3ee3b3e13f4d2cc94abaf8e","tid":1307871,"uid":216421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:40:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人渣</span></span>"},{"pid":"2e8d0594db94b1d82348d46000851301085027a3","tid":1307871,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:41:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5ced1142f3ebb979fbc1226f1958d42312451c6","tid":1307871,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:41:2